Package: parcats
Title: htmlwidget creating plotly parallel categories diagram from easyalluvial plots
Version: 0.0.0.900
Authors@R: person( "Bjoern", "Koneswarakantha", role = c("aut","cre"), email = "datistics@gmail.com", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4585-7799") )
URL: https://erblast.github.io/parcats/
Description: `parcats` adds interactive graphing capabilities to the 'easyalluvial' package.
  The 'plotly.js' parallel categories diagrams offer a good framework for
  creating interactive flow graphs that allow manual drag'n drop sorting of dimensions
  and categories, highlightling single flows and displaying mouse over information. The
  'plotly.js' dependency is quite heavy and therefore is outsourced into a separate package.
